==English==
===Pronunciation===
*SAMPA: /t@"mA:t@U/
===Etymology===
Of [[Nahuatl]] origin, via Spanish.
===Noun===
'''tomato''' (Plural: [[tomatoes]])

#A savoury [[fruit]], red when ripe, treated as a [[vegetable]] in horticulture
#:'''NOTE:''' The US Supreme Court in Nix v. Hedden (1893) ruled that a tomato is a vegetable.
====Taxonomic term====
*'''Lycopersicon esculentum'''

